.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775111862841_ooj9xk7n5wn.jpg","videoUrl":null,"imagePrompt":"A dignified Korean Jindo dog with cream-colored fur sitting upright in front of overgrown bushes and wild grass at a dog park, a muddy tennis ball placed directly in front of his paws, the dog has an alert but calm expression with pointed ears, mature 8-year-old appearance, natural lighting, shallow depth of field with bushes slightly blurred in background, the dog looks proud but nonchalant like a detective who just cracked a case, Australian park setting with eucalyptus trees visible in distant background, square format, 1:1 ratio, photorealistic style\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기.\n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"dog park 에만 가면 어디선가 공을 물어오는 국둥이","createdAt":"2026-04-02T06:37:15.208Z"}]
